Cognis Harvest is an early-prototype analytic tool for illicit-crop estimation.
It operates on supplied or synthetic multispectral/SAR data; it is not a fielded
satellite pipeline. Bundled data is SYNTHETIC. Yield/market coefficients in
data/coefficients.json are ILLUSTRATIVE, not authoritative. Operational use
requires calibrated, region-specific inputs and validation against ground truth.
Use only within your lawful authority.
